org.corfudb.runtime

Class CorfuDBObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.corfudb.runtime.CorfuDBObject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<CorfuDBObject>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CDBListNode, CDBMNode, CDBNode, CorfuDBCounter, CorfuDBList, CorfuDBMap

    public abstract class CorfuDBObject
extends Object
implements Comparable<CorfuDBObject>
    This class must be sub-classed by any new CorfuDB object class. It provides helper code for locking and timestamp bookkeeping. It also defines the abstract apply upcall that every CorfuDB object must implement.
